data.description: Come live in the serenity of this home surrounded by 5 acres (almost 6 with Toddsbury lot of .87) Convenient to Vinton, Downtown Roanoked & the Greenway amenities. Your decompression will start with the ride up Toddbury Dr where mature trees blanket the road.  At the crest of Horsepen Montain sits this 4 BR home offering an abundance of outdoor vignettes. Numerous updates throughout: new windows gutters with leaf guards, engineered hardwood U/L, LTV flooring (E/L & L/L),  hot water tank & water filtern, and recently painted.  A rock accent wall surrounds the fireplace in the family room, bringing the outside in & creates a warm and welcoming environment.  Kitchen island to convey.  Engineered hardwoods on the upper level in the MBR and other bedrooms.  MBR with walk-in closet and plantation shutters.  Walk-out L/L can be used as office space, game/theatre, or work-out area.  Enjoy your morning coffee from the screened-in porch while watching the sun rise, then wind down your day with your favorite beverage im the swing under the deck while taking in the sunset.   City lights and mountain views can be seen in the colorful Fall, Winter and early Spring.  Acres of wooded land for walking and exploring.  An abundance of decking flank two sides of the house for grilling or hot tubbing (hook up available).  A warm fire in the white-pebbled Firepit area will extend your outside season for entertaining.  And to top it all off, there is a climate controlled She/He shed just steps from the house that can be a playhouse, office, storage. She/He shed climate by Mini-split heat pump.
